CAREERS



John G. Ullman & Associates is a different kind of wealth management firm. Our “one firm” model provides high net worth individuals and families a single place to turn for all aspects of their financial needs, including financial planning, wealth management, and “special projects” catered to their unique needs. Our relationships with our clients are long-standing, often spanning decades and multiple generations. Our headquarters are in Corning, New York, in the beautiful Finger Lakes Region, with a second office in Rhinebeck, in the Hudson Valley Region of New York.
We are always interested in growing our team when we have the opportunity to work with the best in our industry. If you are a difference maker, interested in joining a dynamic wealth management team, and would like to pursue a career with John G. Ullman & Associates, please send a letter of interest and your resume to
